snippet.title: Dawnfolk - Launch Trailer | Charmingly Dark Survival City-Builder
snippet.description:
Dawnfolk is a charmingly dark minimalist survival city-builder by Darenn Keller. Collect resources and rebuild your realm one tile at a time as you protect your settlers from oppressive shadows. Can you unveil the secrets of the monoliths to bring light back to the world?

Dawnfolk is available now on PC on Steam.

Buy Dawnfolk now!
⟁ https://store.steampowered.com/app/23...
